                    <li>Latest list of directors with DINs and consent particulars (must be at least 3 post-conversion, 1 Indian resident)</li>
                    <li>Latest audited financial statements of the company (preceding FY)</li>
                    <li>Board resolution authorising the conversion and convening of EGM</li>
                    <li>Notice of EGM with explanatory statement under Section 102; special resolution text; EGM minutes</li>
                    <li>Draft amended MOA (with name change from 'Private Limited' to 'Limited' and other consequential changes)</li>
                    <li>Draft amended AOA (removing share transfer restriction under Section 2(68)(i), 200-member cap and public invitation prohibition)</li>
                    <li>PAN, TAN, GSTIN of the company; bank account details (for post-conversion updates)</li>
                    <li>Consents and DSCs of new directors and shareholders being added</li>
                    <li>Valuation report under Section 247 for fresh share allotment to expand shareholder base (where applicable)</li>
                    <li>Compliance certificate from a Company Secretary in Practice (PCS) confirming all formalities (best practice; recommended)</li>
                </ul>

            </div>
        </div>
